ru.ifmo.ctddev.filippov.parallelmapper

Class IterativeParallelism

  • java.lang.Object
    • ru.ifmo.ctddev.filippov.parallelmapper.IterativeParallelism

  • public class IterativeParallelism
extends Object
    This class represents functions that can be executed simultaneously in the given number of distinct threads.

    It uses functions from IterativeParallelismUtils to parallel it's functions (like foldl and map). Some functions also use implementation of monoid - Monoid class.

    It also uses ParallelMapperImpl to execute tasks on number of threads specified in that object

    See Also:
    IterativeParallelismUtils, Monoid, ParallelMapperImpl
